datasets.Rmd

Dataset Statistics

By Type 

library(kwb.fisbroker)
kwb.fisbroker::fb_datasets %>%  
  dplyr::count(.data$dataset_type) %>% 
  dplyr::arrange(dplyr::desc(.data$n)) %>% 
DT::datatable()

By Type and Category 


kwb.fisbroker::fb_datasets %>%  
  dplyr::count(.data$dataset_type,
               .data$category_name) %>% 
  dplyr::arrange(dplyr::desc(.data$n)) %>% 
DT::datatable()

All Datasets

Dataset Names and Types 

kwb.fisbroker::fb_datasets %>%  
  dplyr::select(-.data$dataset_name_href,
                -.data$dataset_type_href) %>% 
DT::datatable()

Dataset Links 

kwb.fisbroker::fb_datasets %>%  
  dplyr::select(
    .data$dataset_id,
    .data$dataset_name,
    .data$dataset_name_href,
    .data$dataset_type_href) %>% 
DT::datatable()
